SUBMISSION REQUIREMENTS<BR><BR>Three types of submission are solicited: =
full=20
papers, short papers,<BR>and project abstracts.<BR><BR>Full=20
papers<BR>-----------<BR>Full papers are original papers of maximally 12 =
pages,=20
that will be <BR>published in the workshop proceedings and will have a =
full oral=20
<BR>presentation of about 30 minutes at the workshop.<BR><BR>Short=20
papers<BR>------------<BR>Short papers are mini-papers of maximally 4 =
pages,=20
that will be <BR>published in the workshop proceedings and have a very =
brief=20
('flash') <BR>oral presentation at the workshop. Authors of short papers =
are=20
<BR>invited to also put up a poster and participate in a poster=20
session.<BR><BR>Project abstracts<BR>-----------------<BR>Project =
abstracts are=20
brief descriptions of 2 pages of ongoing,<BR>recently completed, or =
starting=20
projects. They will be published in<BR>the workshop proceedings and will =
be=20
presented in a poster session.<BR><BR>Submission=20
formats<BR>------------------<BR>Submission must be done through the =
online=20
submission system at <BR><A=20
href=3D"http://www.easychair.org/IWCS7/">www.easychair.org/IWCS7/</A> =
All=20
submissions should be marked as being <BR>a full paper, a short paper, =
or a=20
project abstract, by adding to the <BR>paper title the postfix (FP), =
(SP), or=20
(PA) when entering the title <BR>of the submission in the online =
submission=20
system. See also the <BR>IWCS-7 website <A=20
href=3D"http://let.uvt.nl/research/ti/sigsem/iwcs/iwcs7">http://let.uvt.n=
l/research/ti/sigsem/iwcs/iwcs7</A>=20
for <BR>information on submission formats. <BR>The page limits =
presuppose=20
standard 11 point Computer Modern font. <BR>Final versions of accepted=20
contributions will have to be submitted <BR>as LaTeX source files to =
facilitate=20
publication of the proceedings; <BR>we also aim at publishing a =
selection of=20
accepted papers in book form<BR>after the workshop.<BR><BR>Online =
submission=20
website: <A=20
href=3D"http://www.easychair.org/IWCS7/">www.easychair.org/IWCS7/</A><BR>=
<BR>Submission=20
deadlines<BR>--------------------<BR>For full papers the submission =
deadline is=20
25 September 2006; for<BR>short papers and project abstracts the =
deadline is 1=20
November.<BR><BR><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs=
